<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px"><FONT size=1></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 4%"><FONT 
face="Times New Roman" size=2>“<U>Listed Notes</U>” means the Series A Notes and 
the Series B Notes to be issued by the Company in favor of holders of 
Outstanding Notes, and for which the Company will apply to have listed on the 
BCBA or on the MAE and, in the case of the Series A Notes denominated in Euro, 
