    <TD vAlign=top align=left width="15%"><FONT face="Times New Roman" 
      size=2>SECTION&nbsp;6.02.</FONT></TD>
    <TD vAlign=top align=left><FONT face="Times New Roman" size=2><U>About 
      this Agreement and the Court Approval</U> </FONT></TD></TR></TBODY></TABLE>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: -6px"><FONT size=1></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 4%"><FONT 
face="Times New Roman" size=2>The Company and the Participating Creditors agree 
to undertake their best efforts and to fully cooperate in order to obtain Court 
Approval for this Agreement. This does not imply the waiver of any rights or 
legal procedures existing in favor of the Participating Creditors. </FONT></P>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px"><FONT size=1></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 4%"><FONT 
face="Times New Roman" size=2>In addition, in order to comply with the timely 
limitations described hereto, the Company will be bound to file all the judicial 
and administrative proceedings required to obtain Court Approval and the 
Authorizations, as well as to take, in an expeditious way and within the 
procedural terms applicable, every reasonable measure to comply with this 
Agreement. </FONT></P>
<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px"><FONT size=1></FONT>&nbsp;</P>
