<P style="MARGIN-TOP: 0px; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-INDENT: 4%"><FONT 
face="Times New Roman" size=2>The Company may terminate this Agreement at any 
time prior to March 31, 2005 if Telecom Personal has not executed its APE by 
that date, unless the Company has already received Court Approval for this 
Agreement. </FONT></P>
